snippet.textDisplay:
Here's a rundown of why the defenders lost:
1. Mozzie peeked under fire
2. Doc doesn't have acog
3. Doc didn't use his Stim for some reason
4. Mira wasn't anchoring, and just held the garage instead (note that she was still behind her black mirror, so that's something I guess)
5. Cav didn't use her silent step one-hit knockdown punch or her knife
6. Doc wasn't anchoring either

Honestly I have no issue with the actions Pulse decided to take. He did well, especially 1v5.
